summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2018 HONDA CR-V. THE CONTACT STATED THAT THE FUEL IN THE VEHICLE WAS NOT BURNING, WHICH CAUSED FUEL TO SEEP DOWN TO THE OIL. THE DEALER (TOM SCOTT HONDA, 603 11TH AVE N., NAMPA, ID 83687) STATED THAT THEY COULD NOT ASSIST UNTIL A RECALL FOR THE FAILURE WAS ISSUED. THE MANUFACTURER WAS ALSO CONTACTED. THE VEHICLE WAS NOT DIAGNOSED OR REPAIRED. THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 400.
